high_descs: Turn right, go to the counter top beside the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter top.
Turn around toward the microwave and go across to the dining table.
Slice the bread on the dining table.
Walk around the dining table to the end closer to the fridge and across from the pot.
Place the knife on the dining table in the right corner closer to the fridge.
Go around to the front of the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of the bread from end closer to the edge of the table.
Turn around toward the fridge and go to the microwave.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave.
Head back to the dining table.
Place the slice of bread on the dining table beside the knife handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn right and move towards the counter top which is near to sink
Take a knife from the counter top
Turn back and walk straight and move towards right to reach the table
Cut the bread loaf into pieces
Turn left little bit and turn right to reach middle of the table
Put the knife on the right bottom of the table
Turn left and again turn right to reach the bread loaf pieces
Take a bread piece from the bread loaf cut
Turn right and walk straight and turn right to reach the oven
Open the oven and put the bread piece inside the oven and close it. After few seconds open the oven and take the slice out and close the oven
Turn right and walk straight and again turn left to reach the table
Put the bread slice next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Put the bread slice next to the knife

high_descs: Turn right to reach the sink counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Cut the bread with the knife on the dining table.
Head to the right side of the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn left to face the bread on the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right to reach the microwave on the right.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and take it out.
Head right to reach the dining table.
Put the slice of bread on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of bread on the dining table.
